attributes.description:
The KIA Soul is a fantastic cross-over / SUV, that cannot be mistaken for anything else due to its unique character, and funky aesthetics. The Soul CRDi Smart sits at the crest of the Soul line-up, which is very evident once it's seen in the flesh. Finished in a two tone red n white, smash n grab safety film, and 18 inch rims that fill the wheel arches perfectly, makes for one stunning vehicle. The interior is also a wonderful place to be, adorned with gorgeous leather seats (electric driver seat), climate control, as well as a multi-function leather steering wheel featuring cruise control.  As with all KIA's of late, the quality of the fit and finish is simply superb. 
 
Don't miss out. Call us now, or leave your details and we will be sure to call you.
